BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:rw7q9xvQhfxwQKbdBOIpd
SUMMARY:Live Music Happy Hour Joe Casalini Trio
DTSTAMP:20260320T020830Z
DTSTART:20260327T230000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Live Music Happy Hour with the Joe Casalini Trio. T
	he Casalini Trio has played happy hours at the Royal Room since 2019. They
	 play laid-back\, swinging versions of great tunes by Duke Ellington\, Bil
	ly Strayhorn\, Hoagie Carmichael\, Phillip Johnston\, and other great Amer
	ican songwriters of the last 100 years. The happy hour usually lasts about
	 an hour and a half. Good drinks\, good people\, good ambience\, and there
	’s never a cover charge\, although the band often encourages donations to 
	local food banks and other worthy causes.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/
	events/#/details/live-music-happy-hour-joe-casalini-trio/16481659/2026-03-
	27T00
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/live-music-happy-hour-joe
	-casalini-trio/16481659/2026-03-27T00
LOCATION:The Royal Room\, 5000 Rainier Ave South\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:4Llg7h8h-thcaQ4AknOCT
SUMMARY:Making Local Markets
DTSTAMP:20260320T020830Z
DTSTART:20260328T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Making Local Markets Downtown Bothell comes alive with creativi
	ty and community at the Making Local Markets on Saturday\, March 28\, 2026
	\, from 10 AM to 4 PM. This vibrant outdoor market showcases 100\\+ small\
	, local\, handmade businesses\, plus an array of delicious food trucks. St
	roll through the bustling streets\, discover unique finds\, and soak in th
	e lively atmosphere. With pet-friendly vibes\, free parking at City Hall\,
	 and plenty of great bars and restaurants nearby\, it's the perfect way to
	 spend a spring Saturday. Don't miss this celebration of local craftsmansh
	ip in the heart of Bothell!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/detai
	ls/making-local-markets/18291548/2026-03-28T00
